Title: The yellow cover
DateModified: '2019-02-15'
DatePublished: '2019-02-15'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-yellow-cover
SetInCountry: Spain
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Zaida Alcaria
AuthorCountry: Spain
Text: 'Martina leaves the UK after her boyfriend forced her to have an abortion. She
  wants to know more about her Spanish family and decides to go to the south and spend
  time with her grandparents: an excellent cook and a restless traveller. She will
  get to know them between recipes and worldwide stories'
